description:
The package containsWIX (Windows Installer Xml) Toolset v3.14.1  required for Wix#. Wix# is a framework for building a complete MSI by using build script files written with the C# syntax.

Note WiX binaries do not belong to WiX#  and they are licenced by their own licencing agreement.
releaseNotes: It is the same WiX v3.14.1 SDK as in the WixSharp.wix.bin.v3.14.1.0.nupkg, plus localizationfiles in the wixui folder.
title: Wix# (WixSharp) - WiX Toolset Binaries
